{
  "collection": {
    "all_types": [
      "Health",
      "Health & Beauty",
      "Invisibility",
      "Water"
    ],
    "products": [],
    "title": "Sale potions"
  }
}
```

##### Output

```html
The 'Sale potions' collection contains the following types of products:

- Health
- Health & Beauty
- Invisibility
- Water
```

